tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE digital_nomad_contacts (
  contact_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  contact_name VARCHAR(50),
  contact_email VARCHAR(100),
  contact_phone VARCHAR(15),
  contact_location VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE contacts (
    contact_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    first_name VARCHAR(50),
    last_name VARCHAR(50),
    email VARCHAR(100),
    phone_number VARCHAR(20),
    location VARCHAR(100),
    skills TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE collaborations (
    collaboration_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    project_name VARCHAR(100),
    project_description TEXT,
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE,
    contact_id UUID
    FOREIGN KEY (contact_id) REFERENCES contacts(contact_id)
);

CREATE TABLE digital_nomad_contacts (
  contact_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  full_name VARCHAR(50),
  email VARCHAR(50),
  phone_number VARCHAR(15),
  current_location VARCHAR(100),
  profession VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE networking_events (
  event_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  event_name VARCHAR(100),
  event_date DATE,
  location VARCHAR(100),
  description TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE collaborations (
  collaboration_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  project_name VARCHAR(100),
  start_date DATE,
  end_date DATE,
  collaborators VARCHAR(200),
  status VARCHAR(20)
);

CREATE TABLE digital_nomad_contacts (
  contact_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  full_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  email VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  location VARCHAR(50),
  skills TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE professional_collaborations (
  collaboration_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  project_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  partner_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  start_date DATE,
  end_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE contact_connections (
  connection_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  contact_id INT NOT NULL,
  connection_type VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  connection_date DATE,
  FOREIGN KEY (contact_id) REFERENCES digital_nomad_contacts(contact_id)
);

CREATE TABLE digital_nomad_contacts (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    name VARCHAR(50),
    email VARCHAR(100),
    phone_number VARCHAR(20),
    location VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE professional_experience (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    job_title VARCHAR(50),
    company VARCHAR(50),
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE projects (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    project_name VARCHAR(50),
    description TEXT,
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE connections (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    contact_id INT,
    connection_id INT,
    relationship_type VARCHAR(50),
    connection_date DATE
);
